{"tid":163464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 10 越來越多植入式廣告，惹用家不滿","createTime":"2017-03-20T03:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T06:26:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1bea7dc962f78f5306341d8fa7b7aaf360396a3","tid":163464,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:58:36.000Z","msg":"藍骨<br />\n<br />\nWindows 10 推出以來 Microsoft 一直大力推廣，最初的免費升級雖然吸引到部分用家，但其陰濕的升級方式卻引起很多不滿。最近又有人發現 Windows 10 開始出現很多擾人的廣告，影響使用體驗。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一般而言我們很少會預期操作系統上面內置有廣告，不過 Windows 10 就打破了這個規矩。其中最近出現在檔案總管中的 OneDrive 通知，就邀請用家付費使用 Office 365，而工作列則在用家使用 Chrome 的時候會彈出邀請使用 Edge 的通知，或者警告用家有關 Chrome 瀏覽器耗電量大的通知，相當煩人。除了自家廣告之外，Windows 10 也逐漸加入越來越多的軟件，例如 Candy Crush 和 Sling TV 等「免費」軟件（視乎地區而定），雖然這些都可以移除，但仍然是個麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft 以前曾經表示 OEM 電腦廠商自行在 Windows 內加入不必要的軟件，令效能大降之餘也影響使用體驗。現在他們自己也在重蹈覆轍，實在令人失望。不過 Windows 10 在轉變成「免費服務」模式的時候，會加入類似廣告的東西，也就實在不令人意外了。"},{"pid":"826e9eae8b29a9bd5c9444b8c6fbf09e5a2ebdb5","tid":163464,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"每次禁開左下角都見到Microsoft幫隻Game賣廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684b144a863a9ebb5e19b25b18b1b1a150ccf061","tid":163464,"uid":60967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"多都可以閂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce78703050bca6e00de5bd30c7a65d7f7b79710","tid":163464,"uid":60967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多都可以閂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多都可以閂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18b68bdae3eee6bceebad40ef52bc7d4f35c627","tid":163464,"uid":76155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:05:23.000Z","msg":"其實佢講嘅有廣告版本都未出，又如何惹用家不滿呢?<br />\n<a href=\"http://Unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUnwire.hk&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=cd3fda0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Unwire.hk</a> 啲新聞真係成日老作"},{"pid":"4b3019eeeac83e50a6a308f427a600ebbafbc9a7","tid":163464,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:06:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b35564aae21333748275fad674c40033cef255f8","tid":163464,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:12:18.000Z","msg":"咁不滿可以用 linux"},{"pid":"334cefa81760fd1463f660b42aed90b7435a3500","tid":163464,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁不滿可以用 linux</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用mac"},{"pid":"dd28ffe0f977d1c47232ca9f651dae58763f2242","tid":163464,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁不滿可以用 linux</blockquote><br />\n窮撚冇錢買ps4，唯有死返入win10打機"},{"pid":"513970915d8f8c1d37353c1d8922880975861c02","tid":163464,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T05:31:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁不滿可以用 linux</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f342547ddfb72911709508bb4fd9fa05fb6d2c9","tid":163464,"uid":79792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T06:26:47.000Z","msg":"破解版win10就無呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n利申 用緊正版"}]}